com.android.gis

类 Recordset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.gis.Recordset

  • public class Recordset
extends java.lang.Object
    记录集
    记录集是矢量数据集中根据一定的查询条件检索中的对象记录的集合。对于一个数据集，查询条件不同可以得到不同的记录集，记录集还可以对记录中的字段信息进行查询和管理。

      • IsEOF

        public boolean IsEOF()
        判断当前记录指针是否指向记录集中最后一个记录之后
        返回:
        指向最后一个记录后返回true，否则返回false。

      • MoveNext

        public boolean MoveNext()
        将记录指针移动到下一条记录
        返回:
        操作成功返回true，否则返回false
        示例代码:
          DataSource ds = new DataSource();
          ds = workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0);
          String strSQL="type = 'school'";
          DatasetVector dstv = new DatasetVector();
          dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDatasetAt(0);
          Recordset recordset = dstv.queryByGeneral(strSQL);
          String strVal = "";
          if((recordset!=null)&&(recordset.getRecordCount()>0)){
              recordset.moveFirst();
              while(!recordset.isEOF){
                  strVal = recordset.getFieldValueString("name");
                  ......
                  recordset.moveNext();
              }
          }
          dstv.ReleaseRecordset(recordset);

      • GetFieldInfoAt

        public FieldInfo GetFieldInfoAt(int nFieldIndex)
        获取指定序号字段信息
        参数:
        nFieldIndex - 字段序号索引(序号从0开始)
        返回:
        返回字段信息
        示例代码:
          DatasetVector dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDataset("兴趣点");
          Recordset rs = dstv.QueryByGeneral("");
          int nRSCount = rs.GetRecordCount();
          if((rs != null)&&(nRSCount>0)){
              rs.MoveFirst();
              int nFieldCount = rs.GetFieldCount();
              FieldInfo fInfo = new FieldInfo();
              fInfo = rs.GetFieldInfoAt(0);
              String strName = fInfo.fieldName;
              int nType = fInfo.type;
              while(!rs.IsEOF()){
                  int nIndex = rs.GetID();
                  switch(nType){
                      case FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_INT32:{
                          int nVal = rs.GetFieldValueInt(strName);
                          break;
                      }
                      case FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_DOUBLE:{
                          double dVal = rs.GetFieldValueDouble(strName);
                          break;
                      }
                      case FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_BOOLEAN:{
                          boolean bVal = rs.GetFieldValueBool(strName);
                          break;
                      }
                      case FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_CHAR:{
                          char cVal = rs.GetFieldValueByte(strName);
                          break;
                      }
                      case FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_TEXT:{
                          String strVal = rs.GetFieldValueString(strName);
                          break;
                      }
                      default:{
                          break;
                      }
                  }
                  rs.MoveNext();
              }
          }
          dstv.ReleaseRecordset(rs);

      • SetFieldValueInt

        public boolean SetFieldValueInt(java.lang.String strFieldName,
                       int iVal)
        设置指定int型字段的字段值
        参数:
        strFieldName - 字段名称
        iVal - 字段值
        返回:
        设置成功返回true，否则返回false
        备注:
        设置字段值前首先要调用Recordset.edit()将记录集设置为可编辑编辑，编辑后要调用Recordset.update()提交更新
        示例代码:
          DatasetVector dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDataset("兴趣点");
          Recordset rs = dstv.QueryByGeneral("");
          int nRSCount = rs.GetRecordCount();
          if((rs != null)&&(nRSCount>0)){
              rs.MoveTo(4);
              int nIndex = rs.GetID();
              int nFieldCount = rs.GetFieldCount();
              FieldInfo fInfo = new FieldInfo();
              fInfo = rs.GetFieldInfoAt(6);
              String strName = fInfo.fieldName;
              int nType = fInfo.type;
              int nVal = rs.GetFieldValueInt(strName);
              if(rs.edit()){
                  bRt = rs.SetFieldValueInt(strName, 202);
                  rs.update();
              }
          }
          dstv.ReleaseRecordset(rs);

      • SetGeometry

        public boolean SetGeometry(Geometry hGeo)
        编辑当前记录的几何对象
        参数:
        hGeo - 几何对象
        返回:
        操作成功返回true，否则返回false
        备注:
        接口调用前首先要调用Recordset.edit()将记录集设置为可编辑编辑，编辑后要调用Recordset.update()提交更新
        示例代码:
          DataSource datasource = new DataSource();
          datasource = workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0);
          String strSQL="type = 'school'";
          DatasetVector datasetvector = (DatasetVector)datasource.GetDatasetAt(0);
          Point2D p2D = new Point2D();
          p2D = mapView.getCenter();
          GeoPoint geoPoint = new GeoPoint();
          geoPoint.make(p2D.x,p2D.y);
          Recordset recordset = datasetvector.queryByGeneral(strSQL);
          if((recordset!=null)&&(recordset.getRecordCount()>0)){
              recordset.moveTo(2); //将记录指针移到第三条记录
              if(recordset.edit()){
                  recordset.setGeometry(geoPoint);
                  recordset.update();
              }
          }
          datasetvector.ReleaseRecordset(recordset);

      • AddNew

        public int AddNew(Geometry hGeo)
        添加一条新记录
        参数:
        hGeo - 几何对象
        返回:
        操作成功返回1，否则返回0
        备注: 
        添加记录，需要调用Recordset.update()提交更新。添加后可以调用Recordset.getID()获取记录编号
        示例代码:
          DataSource datasource = workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0);
          String strSQL="";
          DatasetVector datasetvector = (DatasetVector)datasource.GetDatasetAt(0);
          Recordset recordset = datasetvector.queryByGeneral(strSQL);
          Point2D p2D = new Point2D();
          p2D = mapView.GetCenter();
          GeoPoint geoPoint = new GeoPoint();
          geoPoint.make(p2D.x,p2D.y);
          int iRtID = recordset.AddNew(geoPoint);
          iRtID = recordset.update();
          datasetvector.ReleaseRecordset(recordset);
